{"tid":2003761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(行動Post-1823 app 用得番）請大家投訴藍店不法行為","createTime":"2020-05-06T04:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T07:01:49.000Z","uid":72431,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3fabeeb94ae8a45bedb49487af6fce0d04d4a4","tid":2003761,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"藍店衛生不佳<br />\n藍店防火通道被擠塞<br />\n藍店有人食煙<br />\n23條街站員工收錢冇報稅<br />\n藍絲YouTuber取得盈利冇報稅<br />\n藍店超過一半人聚集違反防疫指引<br />\n藍店貨物阻街違反道路條例<br />\n藍絲違例泊車<br />\n藍絲亂拋垃圾<br />\n室內吃煙<br />\n藍絲入息太高違反公屋資產審查<br />\n藍絲呃綜緩<br />\n村屋超過三層<br />\nTvb 節目意識不良<br />\n藍絲逃稅<br />\n藍車亂cut線<br />\n藍車無打燈<br />\n藍車近車太近<br />\n藍屋僭建<br />\n<br />\n仲有招牌、簷蓬伸出行人路，泠氣機滴水、佔用後巷、僭建閣樓、或者其他思疑違反建築物條例、消防條例、衛生條例、排汚條例等（廢老提供）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請下載1823 Apps，好好用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n禁幾個鍵就投訴到，又可以匿名，記得要求回覆報告<br />\n有懷疑就去投拆，不要懶惰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fb846c159b1ea81359b249743b2eb9e67ac18e","tid":2003761,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhhhhhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"5a1f21a749271c6599b3997c6abfcc031913110b","tid":2003761,"uid":72431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1823 APP使用教學<br />\n隔離Po 抄的<br />\n<br />\n一有可疑就投訴吧 齊做正直的市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無成本 唔係唔做嘛？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n1823 app 係政府推出嘅投訴/查詢app，但唔係所有政府部門都有參與。有參與嘅有：食環署，房屋署，路政署，勞工處，康文署等等（係唔包括黑警嘅）<br />\n所有投訴提交佢都一定要開file follow up，喺指定日子要處理同答覆，冇得不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n既然食環班契弟咁得閒，係時候俾多d野佢地做啦，大家可以投訴某個公眾地方地下多垃圾，某藍店擺賣阻街等等<br />\n<br />\n教學開始<br />\n<br />\n首先係裝個爛鳩 app<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Oc7EUH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Oc7EUH.jpg&h=04852b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去先填個人資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDkdAtm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDkdAtm.jpg&h=6852f45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人資料填是旦填個名就得，<strong>電話可以唔係填</strong>，但就要填個真嘅email, 聯絡時間可以鳩填，因為佢最多都只係send email俾你，最後tick自動填寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPxrVt2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPxrVt2.jpg&h=909f39d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就正式開file啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHVQCKN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHVQCKN.jpg&h=729f6baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開file最緊要係你俾嘅資料夠清晰，一定要講到時地人事，用point form都冇問題。 我就做左個簡單template:<br />\n<br />\n時間：<br />\n地點：<br />\n事件：<br />\n<br />\n如果有相可以夾相，冇都可以。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGahhLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGahhLJ.jpg&h=e527785f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後喺地圖俾埋個地點就可以提交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkFkZZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkFkZZG.jpg&h=a68bd253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分享下d案例：<br />\n<br />\n食環：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lgk5rHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgk5rHF.jpg&h=358b1e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTcb6HH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTcb6HH.jpg&h=6fcca7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勞記：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZjt8WQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZjt8WQ.jpg&h=eb524cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uFwoXQb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuFwoXQb.jpg&h=e8c0194c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熟法例嘅手足可以挑戰埋其他部門"},{"pid":"c3b76b4ef68ac0de88f973821640c70b8a991956","tid":2003761,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3f60b34e2da4dca5605b0e455195732bd84985d","tid":2003761,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d0b482437f0807f6702135f5a099de34f3c5a705","tid":2003761,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad0a5af8ca69bb78c17eeb2fa87d5a57f8fa7ca4","tid":2003761,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"278064ef0f2ff1d61ecc536e9f7973da658a4cbb","tid":2003761,"uid":246077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:07:46.000Z","msg":"高質巴打，投訴內容清晰，簡而精<br />\n1823同相關政府部門都應該好輕鬆可以handle到你講既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba53e41a162d95b4aa9b636205d5bdcfc62b754a","tid":2003761,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12563001981e31d929dce3caa8d9910a169d73fe","tid":2003761,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51add84ecfae3aefd7ed7903fb2a02b3f0c423eb","tid":2003761,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e66437df3ae9362e21870c3bb3b762076a6db6d",